Istanbul gold exchange volume jumps 68 pct in Jan . Monthly volume on Istanbul ' s gold exchange surged to 21 , 649 kilos in January , up 68 percent from December 1996 , mainly due to persistent free market demand fuelled by lower world prices during the month . According to the Exchange ' s monthly bulletin , 61 percent of the January volume was recorded in lira terms and the rest in dollar terms , unchanged from December . Daily average volume rose sharply to 984 kilos last month from 585 in December . Total volume since the inauguration of the Exchange on July 26 , 1995 has now reached 274 , 890 kilos . 1996 volume was 173 , 960 kilos . - - Istanbul newsroom + 90 - 212 - 275 08 75 
